entries.title_d: Protect the transport from the Black Sun pirates in the area until it can make a hyperspace jump.
entries.title: Corellia System: Escort Transport to safety.
entries.thanks_5: Fantastic! I could have sworn we were done for, thanks again pilot!
entries.thanks_4: I haven't seen such moves since...well never. What ever they pay you, it's not enough pilot.
entries.thanks_3: You CorSec boys are worth every cred they pay you!
entries.thanks_2: Phew, that was a close one. We are almost there, keep your eyes open.
entries.thanks_1: Great job! I see that the CorSec have earned their reputation.
entries.taunt_4: Your moves are those of a Gungan in a desert, prepare to die!
entries.taunt_3: Like taking candy from a kid!
entries.taunt_1: This baby is ours, step out of the way or be destroyed CorSec!
entries.split_quest_alert_fail: \#pcontrast3 Sgt Rhea: < \#pcontrast1 You appear to have hit a little snag out there Captain.  Get patched up and run the patrol route again. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 Sgt Rhea: < \#pcontrast1 You appear to have hit a little snag out there Captain.  Get patched up and run the patrol route again. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.shields_depleted: My shields are failing! Get them off me quickly!
entries.reason_5: We just barely escaped the pirates over in sector OC-3101, they are hot on our tail. Please help us.
entries.reason_4: We just barely escaped the pirates over in sector OC-3101, they are hot on our tail. Please help us.

entries.quest_rendezvous_d: Fly to this point to meet up with the freighter you are escorting.
entries.quest_escort_d: The freighter will make their hyperspace jump from this point.
entries.panic_5: These pirates never give up do they?
entries.panic_4: Those blasted space pirates are incoming!
entries.panic_3: The pirate fighters have caught up, they don't seem afraid of your presence pilot.
entries.panic_2: Pirate fighters inbound! I can't defend against them by myself, please help!
entries.panic_1: Incoming Pirate fighters, keep them off me!
entries.hull_half: We're falling apart over here, do your job pilot!
entries.goodbye_5: Good job pilot! We will take it from here.
entries.goodbye_4: Good job pilot! We will take it from here.

entries.goodbye_1: Good job pilot! We will take it from here.
entries.found_loc: Meeting coordinates uploaded to your nav computer, proceed with haste.
entries.failed_protect: I can't do this on my own, I have to hyper jump out of here. I thought CorSec protected this area!
entries.failed_destroy: You let the Pirates destroy that Freighter! Report to your superior immediately.
entries.complete: Mission accomplished. Good job pilot. Report to your superior for further instructions.
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 No more fighter vessels within sensor range. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_loc: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Arrived at rendezvous. Wait here for Freighter to arrive. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.abort: You have failed due to aborting the mission.
